{"tid":2389904,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我好憎一生懸麵","createTime":"2021-02-01T08:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T09:52:24.000Z","uid":90732,"like":9,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"75f282abbaea284f3aee7a1bc329c36e50fab936","tid":2389904,"uid":90732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:20:23.000Z","msg":"話說我今日就去左食一生懸麵<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KBeeen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KBeeen.jpg&h=13fa8b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特濃豚骨沾麵。湯底濃得黎冇死鹹，同埋應該係魚介豚骨？食落唔算太膩。麵條幼啲，又幾啱呢個厚既湯。叉燒好肥美又有炭香，正！食晒料頭加湯飲埋個沾麵汁，好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麵如果多啲麵粉香就一百分！<br />\n<br />\n咁食完之後我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就share比女神bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：今日lunch食左沾麵好正<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：邊間？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：叫一生懸麵，喺旺角<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：個名日文食廣東話字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：下？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一生懸命 &gt; 一生懸麵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：你get唔get到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔明<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6AZqq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6AZqq2.jpg&h=eb9cfb7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：姐係佢哋用黎講自己好用心做麵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係咪我太1999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：？？？......Yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我而家真係好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要食個咁難get到既pun"},{"pid":"f6873eca53654147cc7561680922ab2472bd8ff4","tid":2389904,"uid":14518,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔：食左飯未？<br />\n女：食左<br />\n連登仔：食咩飯？<br />\n女：麵<br />\n連登仔：食咩麵<br />\n女：拉麵<br />\n連登仔：咩拉麵？<br />\n女：一蘭拉麵<br />\n連登仔：有冇加辣？<br />\n女：冇加<br />\n連登仔：點解唔加辣？<br />\n女：唔中意<br />\n連登仔：唔加辣幾錢？<br />\n女：唔過一百，唔講住喇返緊屋企<br />\n連登仔：而家先返屋企？<br />\n女：食完野未返<br />\n連登仔：坐咩車返屋企？<br />\n女：巴士<br />\n連登仔：幾號巴士？<br />\n女：680<br />\n連登仔：680過海？<br />\n女：係<br />\n連登仔：680車錢幾多？<br />\n女：真係唔講住喇<br />\n<br />\n連登仔：返到屋企？<br />\n女：到<br />\n連登仔：而家先返到？<br />\n女：沖涼，唔傾住<br />\n連登仔：你沖涼用咩沐浴露？<br />\n女：Lux<br />\n連登仔：哩隻牌子幾錢？<br />\n女：唔記得<br />\n連登仔：你沖涼沖頭定身先？<br />\n女：頭<br />\n連登仔：沖涼會捽個身幾多下？<br />\n女：一百下<br />\n連登仔：你有數住？<br />\n女：冇<br />\n連登仔：咁你又知？<br />\n女：估<br />\n連登仔：點估？<br />\n女：亂估<br />\n連登仔：亂估都估到？<br />\n女：唔講喇好攰<br />\n連登仔：點解攰？<br />\n女：OT<br />\n連登仔：唔辭職？<br />\n女：唔辭<br />\n連登仔：點解唔辭？<br />\n女：唔想<br />\n連登仔：辭啦<br />\n女：OK<br />\n連登仔：辭左未？<br />\n女：未<br />\n連登仔：幾時辭？<br />\n女：訓喇我<br />\n連登仔：咁夜訓？<br />\n女：係<br />\n連登仔：仲未訓？<br />\n女：覆緊你<br />\n連登仔：咁夜仲覆？<br />\n女：真係訓<br />\n連登仔：仲On緊？<br />\n連登仔：掛住我訓唔著？<br />\n連登仔：唔好諗太多我<br />\n女：好"},{"pid":"8c062a262616b8340ed84be32ddf77579f2a5d0b","tid":2389904,"uid":90732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6873eca53654147cc7561680922ab2472bd8ff4","tid":2389904,"uid":14518,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔：食左飯未？<br />\n女：食左<br />\n連登仔：食咩飯？<br />\n女：麵<br />\n連登仔：食咩麵<br />\n女：拉